हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: A fallen culinary legend walks away from fame to rediscover the true meaning of food and life. In a world chasing perfection, he finds greatness in simplicity. The Missing Master Chef — where every meal tells a story of heart, humility, and redemption
